---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			.hero {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				min-height: 70vh;
				padding: 2rem 1rem;
			}
			.ascii-flow {
				font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
				font-size: 0.78rem;
				line-height: 1.45;
				white-space: pre;
				color: var(--text-color, #333);
				user-select: none;
			}
			.ascii-flow a {
				color: inherit;
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: color 150ms ease;
			}
			.ascii-flow a:hover {
				color: var(--accent-color, #2563eb);
			}
			.ascii-flow .node {
				font-weight: 700;
			}
			.ascii-flow .link-node {
				font-weight: 700;
				border-bottom: 1px dashed currentColor;
			}
			.tagline {
				margin-top: 2rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--muted-color, #666);
				text-align: center;
				max-width: 560px;
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			.tagline a {
				color: inherit;
				text-decoration: underline;
				text-underline-offset: 2px;
			}

			@media (max-width: 700px) {
				.ascii-flow {
					font-size: 0.52rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="ascii-flow" role="img" aria-label="how the system works: sessions produce captures, review sessions produce lessons and rules, everything is measured">
{`  most sessions                   some sessions are review sessions
 в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ                    в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
 в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ                    в”Ӯ                                  в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ  `}<a href="/work" class="link-node">work</a>{`    в”Ӯ                    в”Ӯ  look back at recent `}<a href="/capture" class="link-node">captures</a>{`     в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ                    в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ                        в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ    в–ј     в”Ӯ                    в”Ӯ         в–ј                        в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ `}<a href="/capture" class="link-node">capture</a>{`  в”Ӯв”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җ в”Җв–¶в”Ӯ  spot a pattern (`}<a href="/review" class="link-node">review</a>{`)         в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  learning          в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ                        в”Ӯ
 в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  carries           в”Ӯ         в–ј                        в”Ӯ
      в”Ӯ        forward           в”Ӯ  change the process (`}<a href="/improve" class="link-node">improve</a>{`)  в”Ӯ
      в–ј                          в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ                        в”Ӯ
 в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ                    в”Ӯ         в–ј                        в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ next     в”Ӯв—Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ӯ  new lesson or rule              в”Ӯ
 в”Ӯ session  в”Ӯ  inherits the      в”Ӯ         в”Ӯ                        в”Ӯ
 в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  improvement       в”Ӯ         в–ј                        в”Ӯ
                                 в”Ӯ  `}<a href="/history" class="link-node">measure</a>{` whether it worked       в”Ӯ
                                 в”Ӯ                                  в”Ӯ
                                 в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ`}
				</div>
				<p class="tagline">
					most sessions just work and capture.<br>
					some sessions step back and review the pattern across many.<br>
					those produce the lessons and rules that make future sessions better.<br>
					<a href="/history">how the system evolved</a>
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
